{
  "stem": "53.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't know they were getting into this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know either because we-- when we went into the same rooms every other day or whatever, we didn't know that it's going to be gas or water.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was just pure luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those thousands of women and men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mostly women.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in there, never get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was daily life, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the morning, [INAUDIBLE] in the morning you have to get up and stand in line, whether it rains or it snows or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You didn't have shoes, doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had holes in your shoes, didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Food, they gave you a coffee in the morning and they gave us, they called it a kommissbrot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Bread which cuts in four pieces for four people in 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was my daily life in Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm not talking about beating up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If any German wants to, he went by and he didn't like your face, he beat you up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were very, very rude and they were murderers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They killed in Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If there was somebody left alive, a limping one which didn't limp so much, and they caught him in the eye, they have him kneed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they knocked him, a bullet in his neck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was the daily life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was normal life for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We got used to that kind of life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We came in to work and we did what we had to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we've been treated like worse than slaves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I cannot describe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Slave work-- slaves-- and they worked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They got beaten, but they didn't get killed, as I understand, here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They didn't kill them as much as we got killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
